snippet.title: Air Guitar Warrior for Kinect - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Step inside the game and control the music with your own air guitar moves! Choose to play slow or fast, rhythm or lead, or unleash rapid-fire shredding. The lead guitar responds to your playing style! Out now on Xbox One: https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/store/p/air-guitar-warrior-for-kinect/bw1v96v2x5xb
http://airguitarwarrior.com
Official trailer: https://youtu.be/1sQYxOqGsxM
Soundtrack preview: https://youtu.be/xbhJRHKA7C8
